title: You've Never Seen A Mouse Do This...
description:
Contour Unimouse (USA Link) - http://amzn.to/2ACt6AV
Contour Unimouse (International) - http://geni.us/UMRCdHR

The Contour Unimouse (Wireless (also comes in wired variant)) is the most unique computer mouse I've ever used. It features complete adjustability of angle for an experience you can switch on the fly. Can the Contour Unimouse wireless replace my beloved Logitech MX Master 2S? Time will tell...
